<Page name="NFAQ2">
	<size>Big</size>
	<color r="0" g="1" b="0"/>
	<Text>             Eternal Lands Help</Text><nl/>
	<Text>                 Newbie FAQ</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<size>Medium</size>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I EAT/READ A BOOK?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/>
	<Text>Click the use icon at the bottom, then click a food item.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I KNOW WHAT LEVEL I AM?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/>
	<Text>Click the bars icon (stats icon) on the HUD (bottom bar).</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I SEE MY INVENTORY?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Click the bag icon (inventory icon) on the HUD.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I WALK?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/>
	<Text>Use the walk icon, and click on the ground where you want to</Text><nl/>
	
	<Text>move.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I SIT?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Click the second icon from the left, or use alt-s.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>CAN YOU GIVE ME FREE STUFF?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Please, don't ask this in the game! It only gets people</Text><nl/>

	<Text>annoyed at you. </Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I LOOK AT THE MAP?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Press the TAB key, or click on the map icon on the HUD.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.9" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Page: 1</Text><color>yellow</color>
	<link ref="NFAQ3" title=" 2"/><nl/>
	<Text>                     </Text><link ref="HelpPage" title="Back To Help Index"/>
</Page>
<Page name="NFAQ3">
	<size>Big</size>
	<color r="0" g="1" b="0"/>
	<Text>             Eternal Lands Help</Text><nl/>
	<Text>                 Newbie FAQ</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<size>Medium</size>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>WHERE CAN I GET A SWORD OR ARMOR?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>FROM A BLACKSMITH OR FROM PLAYERS, BUT YOU WILL NEED GOLD </Text><nl/>
	<Text>COINS FIRST. (DON'T BEG!)</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>IS {BLANK} PERK GOOD TO HAVE?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Read the wraith's description and decide for yourself.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>CAN YOU HEAL ME?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Don't ask people that. They will heal you if they want to.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I GET MONEY?</Text><nl/>                    
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Kill rabbits and sell the meat and furs to taverns.</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I COOK RAW MEAT?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>You need to Cook it on the campfire, it takes wood and fire </Text><nl/>
	<Text>essence to start a fire (For a long explanation click</Text><link ref="CampF" title=" here"/>
	
	<Text>.)</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.1" g="0.5" b="1"/><Text>HOW DO I GET A FIRE GOING ON ISLA PRIMA?</Text><nl/>
	<color r="0.5" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><link ref="FireB" title="Click here for a step-by-step walkthrough"/><Text>.</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<color r="0.9" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text>Page:</Text><color>yellow</color>
	<link ref="NFAQ2" title=" 1"/><color r="0.9" g="0.9" b="0.9"/><Text> 2</Text>
	<color>yellow</color><nl/>
	<Text>                     </Text><link ref="HelpPage" title="Back To Help Index"/>
</Page>
<Page name="CampF">
	<size>Big</size>
	<color r="0" g="1" b="0"/>
	<Text>             Eternal Lands Help</Text><nl/>
	<Text>             How to cooking meat</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<size>Medium</size>
	<color r="1" g="0.5" b="0"/><Text>To cook meat: </Text><nl/><nl/>
	<color r="0.9" g="0.9" b="0.9"/>
	<Text>1. Find a burning campfire (There is one on IP near the beam </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   up point).</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<Text>2. Open your inventory and right click with your mouse over </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   the raw meat until the "use with" pointer comes up. (Looks </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   like a fist). </Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<Text>3. Click and drag each piece of meat onto the burning fire. </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   Placement is critical and somewhat touchy at times. If </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   you've succeeded the words "You've cooked the meat!" will </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   appear on your screen. If not then keep trying.</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<nl/>
	<nl/>
	<nl/>
	<nl/>
	<Text>                            </Text><color>yellow</color><link ref="NFAQ3" title="Back To FAQ"/>
	<nl/>
</Page>
<Page name="FireB">
	<size>Big</size>
	<color r="0" g="1" b="0"/>
	<Text>             Eternal Lands Help</Text><nl/>
	<Text>                Basic Campfire</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<size>Medium</size><color r="1" g="0.5" b="0"/>
	<Text>If the fire is not burning:</Text><nl/><color r="0.9" g="0.9" b="0.9"/>
	<nl/>
	<Text>1. Harvest some logs. (Some can be found on the west end of</Text><nl/>
	<Text>   one of the buildings to the south of the campfire.) You will </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   about four logs in total.</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<Text>2. Return to the campfire and load the logs into the firepit </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   by clicking the "Use with" icon (closed hand), clicking on logs,  </Text><nl/>
	
	<Text>   and then clicking on the campfire. If successful you should   </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   see the words"You put some logs on the fire". Repeat until</Text><nl/>
	<Text>   it says "You cannot put anymore logs on the fire!"</Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<Text>3. Ignite the fire using a fire essence just like you </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   loaded the firepit with logs earlier. If you do not have </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   fire essence you can make some or buy some form the magic </Text><nl/>
	<Text>   shop(15 gc each) or buy from market channel (#jc 3). </Text><nl/>
	<nl/>
	<nl/>
	<Text>                     </Text><color>yellow</color><link ref="NFAQ3" title="Back To FAQ"/>
	<nl/>
</Page>
</Help>
